@startuml
autonumber
skinparam Style strictuml

actor User
participant "System" as Sys
database "Database" as DB

User -> Sys: Enters company email and password
User -> Sys: Clicks "Sign In" button
activate Sys

Sys -> Sys: Validates input format
Sys -> DB: Requests user credentials
activate DB

DB -> DB: Searches for user record
DB --> Sys: Returns user data, hashed password, and role
deactivate DB

alt Credentials valid? (yes)
    Sys -> Sys: Generates session token
    Sys -> Sys: Determines Role (Admin, Lead, or Employee)
    Sys -> Sys: Redirects to role-specific Dashboard
    Sys --> User: Displays home page
else Credentials valid? (no)
    Sys -> Sys: Clears password field
    Sys --> User: Displays "Invalid Credentials" message
end

deactivate Sys
@enduml